[SN]TITLE[SN]
Winter Olympics 2018: All you need to know a year to go

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
There's exactly one year to go until the Winter Olympics officially kick off in the Asian country of South Korea.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
9 February 2017 Last updated at 15:00 GMT
Thousands of athletes from around the world will be going for glory on the ice and snow.
So what events will there be, how many medals are up for grabs and what will the mascots look like?
Here's Ayshah with all you need to know!
